            <div type="translation">
                <p>Abraham, Abraham. Do not lay your hand on the child. Do not do anything to him.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Poor Condition. The painter's writing seems to have been influenced by spoken language. Τhe common nu of the cypriot dialect was added at the end of the word χεῖρα. Accents and breathings with errors. Text: Gen. 22:12.</p>
            </div>
